  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized, three-arm, double-blind, placebo-controlled, Phase III clinical trial
      of caffeinated gum and sugar-less gum in adult patients after an abdominal procedure.
      Patients will be randomized to receive placebo, sugar-less gum or caffeinated gum three times
      daily for 30 minutes starting the day following surgery until discharge or 24 hours after
      attainment of the primary endpoint.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
