  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Abdominal procedure (Laparoscopic or open, occurring electively), American Society of
             Anesthesiologists (ASA) physical status score ≤ 3, Glasgow Coma Score (GCS) ≥ 15.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  ASA physical status score of &gt;3, GCS &lt; 15, complete bowel obstruction, history of
             cardiac arrhythmia, history of phenylketonuria, alcohol abuse. substance abuse
             dentures
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
